        "html_content": "\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; font-size: 0.75em; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">*<span>\u00a0</span></span></span></sup>Section\r\n        63. Assessment of unregistered persons.-</strong></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Notwithstanding\r\n      anything to the contrary contained in<span>\u00a0</span><a alt=\"section 73\" href=\"http://taxinformation.cbic.gov.in/content-page/explore-act/1000347/1000001\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(62, 138, 204); cursor: pointer;\" target=\"_blank\">section\r\n        73</a><span>\u00a0</span>or<span>\u00a0</span><a alt=\"section 74\" href=\"http://taxinformation.cbic.gov.in/content-page/explore-act/1000348/1000001\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(62, 138, 204); cursor: pointer;\" target=\"_blank\">section\r\n        74 <sup>1</sup>[or section 74A]</a>, where a taxable person fails to\r\n      obtain registration even though liable to do so or whose registration has\r\n      been cancelled under sub-section (2) of<span>\u00a0</span><a alt=\"section 29\" href=\"http://taxinformation.cbic.gov.in/content-page/explore-act/1000298/1000001\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(62, 138, 204); cursor: pointer;\" target=\"_blank\">section\r\n        29</a><span>\u00a0</span>but who was liable to pay tax, the proper\r\n      officer may proceed to assess the tax liability of such taxable person to\r\n      the best of his judgment for the relevant tax periods and issue an\r\n      assessment order within a period of five years from the date specified\r\n      under<span>\u00a0</span><a alt=\"section 44\" href=\"http://taxinformation.cbic.gov.in/content-page/explore-act/1000315/1000001\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(62, 138, 204); cursor: pointer;\" target=\"_blank\">section\r\n        44</a><span>\u00a0</span>for furnishing of the annual return for the\r\n      financial year to which the tax not paid relates:</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: Poppins; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Provided<span>\u00a0</span></strong>that\r\n      no such assessment order shall be passed without giving the person an\r\n      opportunity of being heard.</p>\n<div class=\"footnotes\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); font-weight: 400; padding-top: 15px; color: blue; font-size: 12px !important; font-family: Poppins; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">*Enforced w.e.f. 1st July, 2017.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">1. </span><span _ngcontent-tkt-c153=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: Poppins; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span _ngcontent-tkt-c153=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span _ngcontent-tkt-c153=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span _ngcontent-tkt-c153=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Inserted<span>\u00a0</span></span></span></span></span></span><span _ngcontent-tkt-c153=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: Poppins; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span _ngcontent-tkt-c153=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span _ngcontent-tkt-c153=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span _ngcontent-tkt-c153=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span _ngcontent-tkt-c153=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">by\r\n                    section 131 of\u00a0 The Finance Act (No. 2) Act, 2024 No.\r\n                    15 of 2024 dated 16.08.2024.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n",
        "source_url": "https://taxinformation.cbic.gov.in/content/html/tax_repository/gst/acts/2017_CGST_act/active/chapter12/section63_v1.00.html",
        "section_title": "Assessment of unregistered persons"
